trans-unit.source: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute marks a component's visibility.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute markerar en komponent synlighet.

trans-unit.source: If <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.Yes"></xref> is present, a visual designer can show this component on a designer.
trans-unit.target: Om <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignTimeVisibleAttribute.Yes"> </xref> finns en visuell designer kan du visa den här komponenten i en designer.

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeVisibleAttribute is a hint to the Designer.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute är en ledtråd Designer.

trans-unit.source: The Designer will ignore this attribute for components that have a UI presence.
trans-unit.target: Designern kommer att ignorera det här attributet för komponenter som har ett användargränssnitt förekomst.

trans-unit.source: It can only be applied to classes.
trans-unit.target: Det går endast att använda klasser.

trans-unit.source: The DesignTimeVisibleAttribute is most useful when you have a control that accepts child components.
trans-unit.target: DesignTimeVisibleAttribute är mest användbart när du har en kontroll som accepterar underordnade komponenter.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> control's node items should not appear in the component tray because they are drawn by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> control.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>kontrollens nod objekt ska inte visas i komponenten fack eftersom de ritas genom de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeView?displayProperty=fullName>
